Package org.jboss.windup.reporting.rules.rendering

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CssJsResourceRenderingRuleProvider  
    ExecutionTimeReportRuleProvider
    Produces a simple text report of how long each RuleProvider's rule took to execute, the time spent in each phase, and any other timing data that was been stored in ExecutionStatistics.
    RenderGraphRuleProvider
    This renders the graph itself to the output directory for debug purposes.
    RenderReportRuleProvider
    This renders the ApplicationReport, along with all of its subapplications via freemarker.
    RenderRuleProviderReportRuleProvider
    Renders a report of all AbstractRuleProviders that were loaded by Windup, as well as the results of each Rule execution.
    RenderTagsJavaScriptRuleProvider
    This renders the data of tags into a .js file, which is later linked from various report pages.
